The paper discusses automatic attribute discovery methods for visual descriptions, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed metric for evaluating attribute meaningfulness is based on machine learning techniques, such as clustering and classification, which are also relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions datasets and user studies, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
